          <img class="mobile-img" src="https://usa-oss.edifier.com/Uploads/images/2022/06/23/2022062309534816559492283786.jpg" alt="" />
          <div class="banner-item-content">
            <p class="title">CREATOR</p>
            <p class="title">MEETS</p>
            <p class="title">EDIFIER</p>
            <p class="desc">“A passion for sound” has been Edifier’s tagline for years, and creativity is where the brand value lies. Edifier never limits its imagination in technological innovations and has been focused on creating classic yet unique audio designs. </p>
            <p class="desc">And, we believe that creativity works inextricably with music. many musicians, artists and designers verify the importance of being inspired by music in their creative processes. That is the reason why Edifier has been dedicated to design and produce high-quality audio products, to deliver great music, and to inspire the growing global creators.</p>
