        <p class="aniview desc" data-av-animation="fadeInUp delay-4">Creation is the way that people discover the world with their imagination.</p>
        <p class="aniview desc" data-av-animation="fadeInUp delay-6">Here, EDIFIER  has cooperated with 7 independent “Creators” to showcase their stories, values, music lists, and their way of discovering the world, to represent the brand and to inspire more.</p>
      </div>

